description: The General had a very bad mood this morning. Some client called him on his private mobile. I was out of office. And as the client called already 4 times our secretary decided to give him The General´s number. To make it short - he finally calmed down again. And he made an appointment with the guy this evening. The place where this young guy lived was really dark and lousy. Not even the light in the floor was working. He had to walk upstairs to even see his client´s face the first time properly. He told me that he wasn´t really his type of guy. So he decided to make it even more hard and humiliating. The poor boy had to kiss his feet, to dance and to strip. This must have been a totally shocking meeting.
title: Debt Dandy 10
